After defeating the Anunnaki Resistance attack of 10,500 BC, and assisting the races of Egypt to rebuild their cultures, the Sir- ian Council and guardian allies of humanity continued to visit and assist the evolving cultures, serving as a counterbalance to the Anunnaki Resistance and Templar-Annu forces that continued to assert their inﬂuence on Earth. The new teleport station of the rebuilt pyramid of Giza, now aligned with the energetic systems of Alcyone and the Pleiades, offered swift guardian inter- vention and protection of Earth and easy access to Earth visitation.
